12
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:54.740
Let's go ahead and download the binaries.

13
00:00:54.740 --> 00:00:57.960
Click on the ZIP file over here.

14
00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:04.540
Then, click on this link to download it from the suggested mirror site.

15
00:01:04.540 --> 00:01:06.550
The download should start soon.

16
00:01:06.550 --> 00:01:11.060
Once it's downloaded, unzip it,

17
00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:16.440
and you should see a bunch of JAR files like this.

18
00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:21.120
Now, open up your Java project in the ID.

19
