click on the plus mark over here, select Java.

22
00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:40.890
Now, browse to the JAR files that you downloaded.

23
00:01:40.890 --> 00:01:45.520
Add them one by one.

24
00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:51.570
And finally, click Apply and OK.

25
00:01:51.570 --> 00:01:56.340
Now, when you expand External Libraries,

26
00:01:56.340 --> 00:02:01.240
you can see that the JARs are added to the project.

27
