which is the latest version at the time of recording this course.

34
00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:39.840
You should specify whatever the latest available version number here.

35
00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.640
Now, when you load Maven changes,

36
00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:47.140
it's going to automatically download the dependencies for you.

37
00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:55.840
